text:
East 58th Street, (center of view) between Snyder (right) and Tilden (left Aves. (general view) west from East 59th Street to King's Highway, showing a rear view of two large homes facing the Highway, occupied, from left to right, by Jacob D. Remsen and Teunis Schenck Remsen.

1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
